allowMultipleDns:whether finding multiple DNs should throw an exception (true|false)
baseDn:base dn
connectionFactory:fully qualified class name that implements org.ldaptive.ConnectionFactory
derefAliases:how to handle aliases (NEVER|SEARCHING|FINDING|ALWAYS)
followReferrals:how to handle referrals (true|false)
subtreeSearch:whether to search for the user using a subtree search (true|false)
userFilter:LDAP filter to search for the user
userFilterParameters:LDAP filter parameters to apply to the userFilter
